entities.name: Introduction
entities.description:
# Welcome to the Nimble Design System Package (DSP)
This package collects, organizes, and exports design tokens for use in NI brand components. 

# Start editing
As a DSP creator, you can enter **Edit mode** by clicking on the **Start editing** button at the bottom left. When you finish editing your docs, tokens, or components, please click on **Finish editing**. Adobe XD for Visual Studio Code will then compile your tokens to platform-specific code, and then you will be able to share the DSP package with your team.

You can edit the settings of your package on the "DSP settings" button, and to load a new DSP please click on the package icon at the top left.
